{
  "schema_version": "1.0",
  "description": "Master FS structure seed — CORPORATE (telecom) archetype — STRUCTURE ONLY, no amounts ever. AI-PROPOSED / UNCONFIRMED. tc_* namespace. Seeded from Etihad Etisalat Company (Mobily) FY2024 published FS. Current/non-current presentation. Authored to the Slice-A engine-block contract.",
  "provenance_seed": "ai_proposed_unconfirmed",
  "seed_corporates": [
    "mobily"
  ],
  "extensible": true,
  "extension_method": "propose_confirm_store",
  "notes": [
    "One canonical concept per line; client's own label preserved for display via label_aliases.",
    "A client FS renders ONLY the concepts its TB populates; unused concepts are omitted.",
    "A new corporate maps its lines into these concepts BY SIGNAL; a line matching no concept is PROPOSED as a new concept, confirmed by a human, appended.",
    "NEVER stores amounts. Amounts live with each client's TB, not here.",
    "AI-PROPOSED / UNCONFIRMED: generated from Mobily's published FS, NOT human-approved. Before use this requires (a) human review + an approved xlsx spec, (b) a human-authored master_fs_rollups_authored_corporate.json, (c) GATE 0 (JSON<->xlsx) + rollup fidelity to pass.",
    "Current/non-current split is carried in l0_section. Lines that exist in BOTH maturities (borrowings, lease liabilities, contract assets/costs/liabilities, financial & other assets/liabilities) are DISTINCT concepts split by maturity, not duplicates.",
    "SIGN CONVENTION (proposed): expenses/zakat/tax stored NEGATIVE, mirroring the published statement, so subtotals use '+' on already-negative values. This assumes the published-FS convention; the REAL client TB sign convention is UNCONFIRMED and must be recorded per-client at confirm time. If a real TB stores them positive, the component signs flip.",
    "pl_eps is a non-summing memo leaf (whitelisted by the orphan-leaf guard, same as the bank master).",
    "tc_* namespace — distinct from the bank seed's bs_/pl_/oci_ ids (no cross-seed collision).",
    "engine block authored to the Slice-A loader contract; validates against validate_engine_meta.",
    "Still UNCONFIRMED: requires human review + GATE 0 (JSON<->xlsx) + a human-authored telecom rollups file before it may enter the registry."
  ],
